
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:15,360
"Ashes of Love"



00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:17,240
"Episode 58"



00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:43,020
Mi,



00:02:45,150 --> 00:02:45,920
I have an idea.



00:02:46,500 --> 00:02:49,220
The floral chiefs treat you like their own daughter.



00:02:50,850 --> 00:02:51,620
I want to invite them



00:02:51,870 --> 00:02:53,470
to participate in our wedding ceremony



00:02:53,700 --> 00:02:54,900
as the witnesses of our wedding.



00:02:55,170 --> 00:02:57,870
It’s also sort of a way of repaying
them for their care and upbringing.



00:02:58,720 --> 00:02:59,620
What do you think?



00:03:00,950 --> 00:03:01,870
It’s up to you.



00:03:03,100 --> 00:03:05,550
Mi, I have something to show you.



00:03:11,500 --> 00:03:12,070
Mi,



00:03:13,150 --> 00:03:14,370
pick one piece of paper that is best-looking



00:03:14,620 --> 00:03:15,270
for making wedding invitation cards.



00:03:15,970 --> 00:03:17,000
You are Floral Immortal’s daughter.



00:03:17,370 --> 00:03:18,070
So the floral chiefs



00:03:18,600 --> 00:03:20,120
must like the paper you select.



00:03:21,970 --> 00:03:22,770
Actually it’s all the same



00:03:23,700 --> 00:03:24,700
to me.



00:03:25,070 --> 00:03:26,570
Pick any one you like.



00:03:27,570 --> 00:03:28,700
I think it’s more proper that you decide.



00:03:29,770 --> 00:03:30,850
Since it’s for the wedding,



00:03:31,350 --> 00:03:33,200
let’s select the red one,



00:03:33,700 --> 00:03:35,270
which is for joyous events.



00:03:36,670 --> 00:03:37,170
Go ahead.



00:04:02,050 --> 00:04:03,320
This one.



00:04:06,720 --> 00:04:08,420
I’m wondering whether I picked the right one.



00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:10,850
As long as you like it,



00:04:11,350 --> 00:04:12,320
it’s the best one.



00:04:13,950 --> 00:04:14,670
It seems that



00:04:15,350 --> 00:04:16,269
I picked the right one by luck.



00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:31,900
My Lord.



00:04:34,070 --> 00:04:35,000
How is Liu Ying?



00:04:35,820 --> 00:04:37,970
She has been staying in the room
for three days without coming out



00:04:38,450 --> 00:04:39,500
and drinking water.



00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:42,600
I don't know how to persuade her.



00:04:44,100 --> 00:04:45,050
I’ll check whether she is OK.



00:04:48,970 --> 00:04:50,620
Xu Feng. Father.



00:04:51,770 --> 00:04:53,100
Sorry to have made you worry about me.



00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:53,900
Don’t worry.



00:04:54,659 --> 00:04:55,820
I won’t hurt myself,



00:04:58,100 --> 00:04:58,770
because



00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:01,070
I’m pregnant with Mu Ci’ s baby.



00:05:03,650 --> 00:05:06,770
I will pass on this love.



00:05:09,270 --> 00:05:12,570
Father, could you get me some food?



00:05:14,270 --> 00:05:15,520
OK. OK.



00:05:15,770 --> 00:05:17,100
I’ll go to ask the chefs



00:05:17,100 --> 00:05:18,670
to prepare some of your favorite dishes right now.



00:05:24,270 --> 00:05:24,620
Xu Feng,



00:05:25,540 --> 00:05:27,420
this time King of Gu City must
be working in collusion with Run Yu.



00:05:27,420 --> 00:05:28,060
That’s why he took away Mu Ci



00:05:28,060 --> 00:05:29,380
and forced him to make
Spirit-Vanishing Arrow to kill you.



00:05:30,470 --> 00:05:32,520
The battle between us
and Heaven Realm is inevitable.



00:05:33,750 --> 00:05:34,400
Promise me that



00:05:35,470 --> 00:05:37,600
you will let me take revenge for Mu Ci.



00:06:05,970 --> 00:06:08,100
Xu Feng, eat some snacks.



00:06:10,550 --> 00:06:11,370
What happened to you?



00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:14,000
I am fine. You may leave.



00:06:14,820 --> 00:06:16,170
If you are fine, why are you
hiding your hands behind your back?



00:06:16,450 --> 00:06:17,000
Let me check.



00:06:17,100 --> 00:06:18,020
I told you. I’m fine.



00:06:45,850 --> 00:06:46,950
What’s wrong with your ear?



00:06:51,570 --> 00:06:52,870
It’s because of Jin Mi.



00:06:53,870 --> 00:06:56,350
Last time she was determined
to kill me at the Cave of Jiu Ying.



00:06:56,870 --> 00:06:58,400
If you hadn’t arrived in time,



00:06:59,200 --> 00:07:01,350
my condition would be much worse now.



00:07:04,050 --> 00:07:04,550
Xu Feng,



00:07:05,620 --> 00:07:07,470
I have this ugly scar on my ear.



00:07:08,750 --> 00:07:09,970
Will you dislike me for this?



00:07:11,900 --> 00:07:12,700
Absolutely not.



00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:14,820
That's good.



00:07:16,320 --> 00:07:17,220
You have no idea.



00:07:17,520 --> 00:07:19,850
I have always had nightmares since that day.



00:07:20,970 --> 00:07:22,270
You must take revenge for me.



00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:26,420
Alright. You may leave first.



00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:28,270
I have some official affairs to deal with.



00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:30,900
OK then.



00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:32,100
I’m going back now.



00:07:32,940 --> 00:07:33,740
Go to bed early.



00:08:30,900 --> 00:08:32,049
Glazed Pure Fire.



00:08:37,169 --> 00:08:39,270
Xu Feng, you suspect that Sui He lied to you?



00:08:41,020 --> 00:08:42,669
Last time, seeing that uncle was so serious,



00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:45,150
actually I kind of believed what he said.



00:08:46,250 --> 00:08:46,900
Yesterday



00:08:47,750 --> 00:08:49,700
I accidentally found there was a scar on Sui He’s ear



00:08:50,070 --> 00:08:51,600
caused by a Water Ripple Palm.



00:08:51,970 --> 00:08:53,120
She said it was caused



00:08:53,400 --> 00:08:55,200
by Jin Mi at the Cave of Jiu Ying.



00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:56,370
But that scar



00:08:56,870 --> 00:08:57,900
doesn’t seem new.



00:08:58,100 --> 00:08:59,100
It’s very suspicious.



00:09:00,450 --> 00:09:01,950
Water Ripple Palm.



00:09:02,620 --> 00:09:04,100
It is the magic of which the
past Water Immortal was most proud



00:09:04,100 --> 00:09:05,300
when he was alive, isn’t it?



00:09:07,570 --> 00:09:08,470
If



00:09:09,070 --> 00:09:11,420
the murderer who killed
Water Immortal and Wind Immortal



00:09:11,850 --> 00:09:12,850
is really Sui He,



00:09:13,870 --> 00:09:15,150
then can she use Glazed Pure Fire?



00:09:16,450 --> 00:09:17,820
I went to the Cave of Jiu Ying just now.



00:09:18,520 --> 00:09:21,770
And I found there were
some traces of Glazed Pure Fire.



00:09:22,270 --> 00:09:24,520
The power is no worse than mine.



00:09:25,400 --> 00:09:27,570
But Sui He has always been very delicate.



00:09:28,220 --> 00:09:30,600
In addition, she spent a lot of
power nourishing my body.



00:09:31,300 --> 00:09:32,550
How is it possible that



00:09:32,550 --> 00:09:34,000
she has such pure power?



00:09:35,220 --> 00:09:37,450
I do want to find out the
murderer who killed Water Immortal



00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:38,750
and framed me.



00:09:39,150 --> 00:09:41,420
But I don’t want to wrong the innocent people.



00:09:44,050 --> 00:09:46,150
Let’s check it out.



00:09:52,920 --> 00:09:55,050
No! What kind of person I will be if I do so?



00:09:55,050 --> 00:09:56,370
It’s unfair for Mu Ci.



00:09:56,850 --> 00:09:57,870
Xu Feng, don’t worry.



00:09:58,420 --> 00:09:59,620
No matter how good you are to Sui He,



00:10:00,470 --> 00:10:03,170
Mu Ci is the best to me.



00:10:04,100 --> 00:10:05,570
I have never cared about
other people’s gossip about me.



00:10:06,350 --> 00:10:08,700
So you won’t do anyone wrong.



00:10:14,500 --> 00:10:15,100
Stop.



00:10:16,650 --> 00:10:17,750
Why are you stopping me?



00:10:18,120 --> 00:10:19,420
I am a friend of Water Immortal.



00:10:19,820 --> 00:10:21,470
His Majesty has issued the order that



00:10:21,770 --> 00:10:23,550
outsiders should be forbidden to enter Xuanji Palace.



00:10:24,420 --> 00:10:26,270
I am not an outsider. I’m...



00:10:27,050 --> 00:10:27,900
Mi,



00:10:28,520 --> 00:10:30,200
these two guys don’t let me in.



00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:31,120
Don’t be rude to Immortal.



00:10:31,320 --> 00:10:31,900
Stop.



00:10:36,670 --> 00:10:37,320
Immortal.



00:10:39,300 --> 00:10:41,350
He is my friend. Let him in.



00:10:41,820 --> 00:10:43,500
But what about His Majesty’s order?



00:10:43,970 --> 00:10:45,220
If His Majesty blames you,



00:10:45,500 --> 00:10:47,270
let him come to me.



00:10:48,050 --> 00:10:48,700
Yes.



00:10:52,400 --> 00:10:53,120
Let's go.



00:10:56,220 --> 00:10:58,180
"Xuanji Palace"



00:11:00,670 --> 00:11:02,300
Run Yu is really getting
more and more narrow-minded.



00:11:02,820 --> 00:11:03,770
He even forbids me to see you.



00:11:04,250 --> 00:11:06,500
I think he is afraid that you may run away with me.



00:11:07,700 --> 00:11:08,650
Mi,



00:11:09,450 --> 00:11:12,250
are you really so crazy that you are
going to become the Heavenly Empress?



00:11:12,950 --> 00:11:14,050
Let me remind you.



00:11:14,650 --> 00:11:15,850
To be a Heavenly Empress,



00:11:15,850 --> 00:11:17,920
one has to be particularly talented.



00:11:19,220 --> 00:11:21,750
You are kind of mediocre.



00:11:21,750 --> 00:11:23,770
Not that I underestimate you.



00:11:24,700 --> 00:11:25,800
Mediocre?



00:11:27,520 --> 00:11:28,350
I got it.



00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:30,420
You are suggesting that



00:11:31,470 --> 00:11:32,650
my power is weak.



00:11:33,870 --> 00:11:34,820
No. No.



00:11:35,620 --> 00:11:36,350
I know



00:11:36,500 --> 00:11:40,120
your power is much stronger than before.



00:11:40,650 --> 00:11:41,400
But think about it.



00:11:41,850 --> 00:11:43,250
Among all the previous Heavenly Empresses,



00:11:44,420 --> 00:11:47,750
which one is not ruthless and sinister?



00:11:47,750 --> 00:11:49,650
And which one is not a wolf in sheep's clothing?



00:11:50,570 --> 00:11:52,250
I don’t think you have any of these features.



00:11:53,200 --> 00:11:54,450
Not to mention being the future Heavenly Empress,



00:11:54,920 --> 00:11:56,120
you can’t even compare with Sui He



00:11:56,750 --> 00:11:58,820
in terms of these features.



00:12:03,550 --> 00:12:04,650
Don't be sad.



00:12:05,050 --> 00:12:06,120
I didn’t mean to belittle you.



00:12:09,820 --> 00:12:10,800
I mean



00:12:11,500 --> 00:12:14,620
you can’t bear comparison with her



00:12:15,150 --> 00:12:16,000
in terms of being sinister and adept at scheming.



00:12:16,570 --> 00:12:17,700
You are right.



00:12:18,800 --> 00:12:19,920
Compared with Sui He,



00:12:21,550 --> 00:12:22,620
I’m too stupid.



00:12:24,370 --> 00:12:25,150
I’m so stupid that



00:12:26,470 --> 00:12:28,670
I took revenge for my father on the wrong person.



00:12:30,020 --> 00:12:31,220
I’m so stupid. Right?



00:12:33,120 --> 00:12:35,420
The sea of suffering is boundless,
but you can see the bank when you turn back.



00:12:36,620 --> 00:12:38,200
How about running away?



00:12:38,470 --> 00:12:40,200
If you would like to have affairs,



00:12:40,550 --> 00:12:41,300
I will take you away.



00:12:41,600 --> 00:12:42,500
Again.



00:12:43,320 --> 00:12:44,350
Don’t talk nonsense.



00:12:45,020 --> 00:12:47,970
Run Yu has also done much for me.



00:12:49,400 --> 00:12:50,650
I won't change my mind anymore.



00:12:51,400 --> 00:12:52,720
Then here’s a question.



00:12:53,620 --> 00:12:55,600
Do you love him?



00:13:06,320 --> 00:13:07,420
If you really marry him,



00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:10,200
then there will be no way back.



00:13:21,070 --> 00:13:21,520
Your Majesty.



00:13:24,800 --> 00:13:26,950
Why did she pick the green one?



00:13:28,900 --> 00:13:30,550
She shouldn’t be color-blinded like this.



00:13:31,370 --> 00:13:32,700
Is it because she is absent-minded?



00:13:33,100 --> 00:13:34,850
Or is it because she bears a grudge against me



00:13:35,420 --> 00:13:37,700
that she deliberately picked
this paper to satirize me?



00:13:39,350 --> 00:13:41,770
Or is there some implied meaning?



00:13:42,900 --> 00:13:44,420
Your Majesty, after hearing what you said,



00:13:45,250 --> 00:13:46,700
I realize that Water Immortal has indeed been



00:13:47,520 --> 00:13:49,000
a little bit strange these days.



00:13:49,920 --> 00:13:50,620
What happened?



00:13:51,100 --> 00:13:52,700
Not long ago, Water Immortal



00:13:52,700 --> 00:13:54,770
planted phoenix flowers at Qiwu Palace.



00:13:55,500 --> 00:13:58,370
But those flowers were gray.



00:13:58,920 --> 00:13:59,650
Really?



00:14:00,720 --> 00:14:01,820
I saw that with my own eyes.



00:14:03,920 --> 00:14:05,350
How come she can’t distinguish colors?



00:14:07,370 --> 00:14:08,170
I see.



00:14:09,420 --> 00:14:10,520
Kuang Lu, you may leave.



00:14:10,970 --> 00:14:11,670
Yes, Your Majesty.



00:14:28,900 --> 00:14:31,650
Mi, you came just at the right moment.



00:14:32,150 --> 00:14:34,400
Kuang Lu brought a dish of
pomegranate cake just now.



00:14:34,750 --> 00:14:35,970
I have had breakfast.



00:14:36,500 --> 00:14:38,050
So you may try it for me.



00:14:38,850 --> 00:14:39,570
Your Majesty,



00:14:39,820 --> 00:14:42,020
Kuang Lu prepared it for you.



00:14:42,300 --> 00:14:43,900
So enjoy it yourself, Your Majesty.



00:14:46,800 --> 00:14:47,570
Actually,



00:14:49,770 --> 00:14:50,470
Kuang Lu



00:14:51,900 --> 00:14:53,900
has been with you for a long time.



00:14:54,450 --> 00:14:55,150
She



00:14:56,120 --> 00:14:57,100
is really very nice.



00:14:58,000 --> 00:14:59,550
I won’t say no if you take concubines.



00:15:00,020 --> 00:15:03,070
You can take concubines as many as you like.



00:15:03,850 --> 00:15:05,450
Thank you for being so considerate to me.



00:15:06,570 --> 00:15:07,120
Mi,



00:15:08,050 --> 00:15:09,100
frankly speaking,



00:15:10,400 --> 00:15:11,870
I’m not afraid that you don’t care about me.



00:15:13,270 --> 00:15:15,120
I’m afraid that you care about
me like this occasionally.



00:15:50,700 --> 00:15:51,220
Xu Feng.



00:15:53,350 --> 00:15:53,870
Xu Feng,



00:15:55,170 --> 00:15:56,120
what happened to you?



00:15:56,370 --> 00:15:57,320
Why is your body so cold?



00:15:57,870 --> 00:15:58,550
Get out.



00:15:59,120 --> 00:16:00,920
What happened, Xu Feng?



00:16:01,400 --> 00:16:04,770
Don’t tell anyone else about this.



00:16:05,150 --> 00:16:06,180
Our wedding day is around the corner.



00:16:06,380 --> 00:16:06,940
But your condition...



00:16:07,700 --> 00:16:08,820
What happened exactly?



00:16:08,970 --> 00:16:10,020
Tell me, okay?



00:16:10,720 --> 00:16:11,820
There is nothing wrong with me.



00:16:12,620 --> 00:16:13,620
I will be OK soon.



00:16:18,200 --> 00:16:18,970
The Golden Elixir.



00:16:19,470 --> 00:16:21,100
Someone must have played
a trick in the Golden Elixir.



00:16:22,220 --> 00:16:22,870
Wait a moment.



00:16:33,300 --> 00:16:34,120
Kuang Lu,



00:16:35,450 --> 00:16:36,270
you came just at the right moment.



00:16:37,800 --> 00:16:40,800
I just recalled that Immortal Tai Si



00:16:41,470 --> 00:16:42,870
had mentioned your marriage on that day.



00:16:43,570 --> 00:16:44,450
I’m thinking about...



00:16:44,450 --> 00:16:46,000
I have made my attitude toward this clear that day.



00:16:48,000 --> 00:16:50,570
Why did you mention this matter again, Your Majesty?



00:16:55,820 --> 00:16:58,400
There are many outstanding fairies in Heaven Realm.



00:16:59,220 --> 00:17:00,400
No matter who you like,



00:17:00,750 --> 00:17:03,350
I will definitely arrange a wonderful marriage for you.



00:17:04,420 --> 00:17:05,700
Your Majesty, why do you insist on this matter?



00:17:07,900 --> 00:17:09,200
Are you going to drive me away?



00:17:12,000 --> 00:17:15,470
I know what you want, Your Majesty.



00:17:17,170 --> 00:17:18,770
I also know clearly the result.



00:17:19,450 --> 00:17:21,200
But I don’t want anything else.



00:17:23,670 --> 00:17:25,800
I just want to stay with you all the time, Your Majesty.



00:17:26,270 --> 00:17:26,920
Kuang Lu.



00:17:26,920 --> 00:17:27,619
Your Majesty,



00:17:29,350 --> 00:17:30,450
I will assume that I have never heard



00:17:31,070 --> 00:17:32,570
what you said today.



00:17:36,970 --> 00:17:38,950
After I step out of this room,



00:17:41,070 --> 00:17:44,220
I will forget everything about this matter.



00:17:45,450 --> 00:17:46,700
Do you agree, Your Majesty?



00:17:50,020 --> 00:17:56,670
I will regard your silence as permission.



00:18:03,920 --> 00:18:04,870
Good night,



00:18:05,470 --> 00:18:06,650
Your Majesty.



00:18:08,220 --> 00:18:09,920
I’m leaving now.



00:19:09,900 --> 00:19:10,620
It seems



00:19:12,120 --> 00:19:13,500
I can't never forget you.



00:20:00,550 --> 00:20:02,380
Why did you trespass Heaven Realm at this time?



00:20:03,020 --> 00:20:03,780
What do you want?



00:20:04,370 --> 00:20:05,600
A straightforward person
does not resort to insinuations.



00:20:06,150 --> 00:20:09,700
You must know clearly why I’m here.



00:20:15,450 --> 00:20:17,060
Your mind is hard to read.



00:20:17,740 --> 00:20:18,940
I really don’t know why you are here.



00:20:30,320 --> 00:20:32,270
If you haven’t done anything that makes you guilty,



00:20:32,970 --> 00:20:34,550
why did you close the door and the windows.



00:20:35,100 --> 00:20:37,950
I just want to save your face.



00:20:38,400 --> 00:20:39,670
I have only one question.



00:20:40,250 --> 00:20:41,770
Did you play a trick



00:20:41,770 --> 00:20:42,400
in the Golden Elixir of Lord Lao?



00:20:56,700 --> 00:20:57,720
I was wondering what it is about.



00:20:59,270 --> 00:21:00,800
It turns out to be this trivial matter.



00:21:06,920 --> 00:21:11,670
I just removed a herb that can
provide internal heat from that elixir.



00:21:12,020 --> 00:21:13,020
Just as I expected.



00:21:14,800 --> 00:21:15,800
In the outside world, people say



00:21:16,120 --> 00:21:18,900
the Heavenly Emperor is
deep in love with Water Immortal.



00:21:19,420 --> 00:21:20,150
But they don’t know



00:21:21,300 --> 00:21:23,620
the Heavenly Emperor even lies to
his loved one and makes use of her.



00:21:24,920 --> 00:21:26,850
You knew that Xu Feng still had one piece of soul.



00:21:27,600 --> 00:21:29,220
You also knew that Jin Mi would
definitely use the Golden Elixir



00:21:29,220 --> 00:21:30,540
to save Xu Feng’s life after she got it.



00:21:31,400 --> 00:21:33,550
You know his body constitution is fire
by nature and he’s afraid of coldness.



00:21:34,020 --> 00:21:35,800
So you deliberately removed the heat of the medicine,



00:21:36,970 --> 00:21:40,000
